gdal-grass: GDAL is a translator library for raster geospatial data formats.
gdal-grass: As a library, it presents a single abstract data model to the
gdal-grass: calling application for all supported formats. This extension
gdal-grass: provides access to GRASS data via GDAL.
gdal-grass:
gdal-grass: This package contains the two standalone GDAL-GRASS GIS drivers,
